<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>duō shǎo nián bù shì yī cì de wèn 迦南438</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 duō shǎo nián bù shì yī cì de wèn, bù shì yī cì de xún,
 yì rén wèi hé duō kǔ nán, yì rén wèi hé duō shāng hén,
 mó lì yōu shāng jǔ jué jiān xīn, liǎn shàng kè mǎn zhòu wén,
 tiě chuāng lèi, qīn rén qì, shì rén wú gù hèn,
 fù shén yào liàn jìng wǒ men nǎ, rú tóng nà guì jīn yín,
 zhī dào yī qiè nǐ huì xiàn shàng gǎn xiè zàn měi shén.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>438</hymn_number>
</song>